    <h3>Parthu</h3>

    <p>This tall 6-9 ft beast can be found protecting its garden of parthu flowers in dark places. It collects corpses for the parthu 
    flowers to grow upon. There is always a Parthu where there are parthu flowers, as it is an evolved form of the flower itself.</p>

    <p>It's weak to flame, and dried terim petals can put it to sleep if thrown at it the moment it tries to suck in spores to 


