    <h5>Skills</h5>
    <p>Double action (passive): 
        <span class="move-description"> This monster can use two active actions per turn.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Spore consumption (active):
        <span class="move-description"> Using the spores of the parthu flowers, the Parthu can rejuvenate 6 vit points per turn.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Strangle (active):
        <span class="move-description"> The Parthu uses its tentacles to strangle a chosen victim.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Stab (active):
        <span class="move-description"> The Parthu stabs a chosen victim with a tentacle.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Drag (active):
        <span class="move-description"> The chosen victim must roll phys to dodge this attack. On a 2 they succeed. If they are 
            dragged, an ally must use a phys skill of 2 to free them, or attack the monster's tentacles. They have a 50/50 chance of 
            attacking the one dragged as well. The one being dragged can attack with a sorc attack if they succeed an aca roll of 1 for 
            focus.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Fire weakness (passive): 
        <span class="move-description"> Any fire attack will do double damage against the Parthu.</span>
    </p>
